SPARK | VISUAL LANGUAGE SPEC  
“Live Circuit – Nervous System”

-------------------------------------------------
1. COLOR TOKENS (Tailwind)
-------------------------------------------------
/* base */
--void-950: #050505;               /* bg-void-950 */
--matrix-400: #00FF41;             /* text-matrix-400 / border-matrix-400 */
--alert-500: #FF3B30;               /* text-alert-500 / border-alert-500 */
--process-300: #FFEB3B;           /* text-process-300 / border-process-300 */

/* glows (drop-shadow) */
--glow-matrix: 0 0 4px #00FF41, 0 0 12px #00FF41;
--glow-alert: 0 0 4px #FF3B30, 0 0 12px #FF3B30;
--glow-process: 0 0 4px #FFEB3B, 0 0 12px #FFEB3B;

-------------------------------------------------
2. TYPOGRAPHY
-------------------------------------------------
font-mono text-matrix-400 text-xs leading-tight tracking-tight  
/* 12-px JetBrains Mono, 1.1 line-height, –0.02em letter-spacing */

-------------------------------------------------
3. CRT OVERLAY (pseudo-element)
-------------------------------------------------
.crt::after {
  content: "";
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(
    0deg,
    rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 0,
    rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px,
    transparent 1px,
    transparent 2px
  );
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 9999;
  animation: scanline 8s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes scanline { to { transform: translateY(100vh); } }

-------------------------------------------------
4. THE NERVOUS SYSTEM – SVG WIRE
-------------------------------------------------
<svg class="w-full h-full">
  <path
    id="wire"
    class="stroke-current"
    vector-effect="non-scaling-stroke"
    stroke-width="2"
    stroke-linecap="round"
    fill="none"
  />
</svg>

Tailwind utility:
.text-matrix-400 { stroke: #00FF41; }
.drop-shadow-glow-matrix { filter: drop-shadow(var(--glow-matrix)); }

-------------------------------------------------
5. FRAMER MOTION STATES
-------------------------------------------------
const wireStates = {
  idle: {
    pathLength: 1,
    opacity: 0.4,
    filter: "drop-shadow(none)",
  },
  processing: {
    pathLength: 1,
    opacity: 1,
    filter: "drop-shadow(var(--glow-process))",
    stroke: "#FFEB3B",
    transition: {
      stroke: { duration: 0.3 },
      opacity: { repeat: Infinity, repeatType: "reverse", duration: 0.6 },
    },
  },
  success: {
    pathLength: 1,
    opacity: 1,
    stroke: "#00FF41",
    filter: "drop-shadow(var(--glow-matrix))",
    transition: { type: "spring", stiffness: 400, damping: 20 },
  },
  failure: {
    pathLength: 0.6,               // break at 60 %
    opacity: [1, 0, 1],
    stroke: "#FF3B30",
    filter: "drop-shadow(var(--glow-alert))",
    transition: {
      opacity: { repeat: Infinity, duration: 0.4 },
    },
  },
};

/* Light-pulse travel */
const pulseVariants = {
  initial: { pathOffset: 0, opacity: 0 },
  travel: {
    pathOffset: 1,
    opacity: [0, 1, 0],
    transition: { duration: 1.2, ease: "linear" },
  },
};

-------------------------------------------------
6. REACT USAGE PATTERN
-------------------------------------------------
<motion.path
  d={pathData}
  variants={wireStates}
  initial="idle"
  animate={status}          // 'idle' | 'processing' | 'success' | 'failure'
/>

{status === "processing" && (
  <motion.circle
    r="3"
    fill="#FFEB3B"
    filter="url(#glow)"
    variants={pulseVariants}
    initial="initial"
    animate="travel"
  />
)}

-------------------------------------------------
7. ACCESSORY CLASSES
-------------------------------------------------
/* blinking cursor */
.blink::after {
  content: "_";
  display: inline-block;
  animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
}
@keyframes blink { 50% { opacity: 0; } }

/* matrix glow text */
.text-glow {
  text-shadow: 0 0 2px #00FF41, 0 0 6px #00FF41;
}

-------------------------------------------------
8. SUMMARY SNIPPET
-------------------------------------------------
<div className="crt bg-void-950 font-mono text-matrix-400 text-xs">
  <svg className="w-full h-full">
    <motion.path
      className="stroke-current"
      variants={wireStates}
      initial="idle"
      animate={status}
    />
  </svg>
</div>

-------------------------------------------------
Drop these tokens & states into Tailwind config, toggle the motion “status” prop, and the schematic lives—green when clean, red when broken, yellow pulse while thinking.

